# Frontend Rules

## Constraints

- **No game logic in UI** — UI displays and forwards input. Engine computes.
- **Component isolation** — Each component has a single responsibility.
- **Game canvas** — Thin adapter to engine; renders state, captures input.

## Structure

- `apps/web/app/` — App Router pages
- `apps/web/components/` — Shared components
- `apps/web/components/game/` — Game canvas layer

## State

- Use Zustand or React Context for session state.
- Never compute level validity in frontend — delegate to engine.
